{"tid":325642,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"水晶宮無懼被龜扑 政府總部冒雨操練","createTime":"2017-07-17T11:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T11:46:07.000Z","uid":9030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5ea07842ec131ed39e8a3404db79abd3c7c1b7","tid":325642,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:18:21.000Z","msg":"水晶宮領隊法蘭迪保亞新官上任三把火！球隊下午1時多抵達香港後，只休息幾個鐘，下晝5點半，喺雷暴警告之下，仍然由君悅酒店徒步10分鐘，行去政府總部添馬公園作輕鬆操練。<br />\n<br />\n由於雨勢愈落愈大，球隊最終只慢跑及拉筋近20分鐘就打道回府。不過，仍然可見法蘭迪保亞軍紀嚴明，備戰認真。"},{"pid":"1919c5d68b6b39c892b29932275dc496456e9e55","tid":325642,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170717/photo/bkn-20170717175440271-0717_00882_001_04b.jpg?20170717184553\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20170717%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170717175440271-0717_00882_001_04b.jpg%3F20170717184553&h=e7431b75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d823edbed6f15e7d3a4d39bf70a38dda7c8c7846","tid":325642,"uid":23323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:27:11.000Z","msg":"下季攞英超大熱"},{"pid":"40a2e7ad63ef2163ce9a94529c3fe795edd8c2e7","tid":325642,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下季攞英超大熱</blockquote><br />\nALL IN左"}]}